==Trivia==
*Sunk 7 August 1944 by torpedoes from submarine [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Croaker_(SS-246) USS ''Croaker'' (SS-246)] off the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amakusa Amakusa Islands], [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/East_China_Sea East China Sea] [http://tools.wmflabs.org/geohack/geohack.php?pagename=Japanese_cruiser_Nagara&params=32_09_N_129_53_E_ 32°09′N 129°53′E].
*Became Admiral Nagumo's flagship after the carrier Akagi was abandoned during the Battle of Midway. Becoming a replacement flagship was a common thing with her.

